    "under five levels of AI governance i.e., team, organization, industry, national, and and non-academic sources (like conference papers and preprints) was useful for obtaining a wider perspective.The search terms resulted in a total of 2918 papers.",
    "The search selection criteria have been applied to the abstracts of 2918 papers to retrieve the most relevant papers.",
    "The inclusion criteria of the year of publication and relevance were applied.",
    "The articles published in English between 2013 to 2023 in Google Scholar, and Scopus were considered while determining inclusion criteria.",
    "Moreover, the papers relevant to the research focus were considered for inclusion, while book chapters and reports were excluded."
